### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json


### Get Products by Category
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products?categoryId={{category_id}}&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Search Products with Filters
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products?search=Latte&type=SIMPLE&isActive=true&sortBy=basePrice&sortOrder=asc
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Products by Category with Search and Filters
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products?categoryId={{category_id}}&search=Latte&type=SIMPLE&isActive=true&sortBy=basePrice&sortOrder=asc
Content-Type: application/json


### Get product by slug
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products/nuoc-ep-cam
Content-Type: application/json
@category_id=215e35bd-517e-457f-ad04-f4957de88b59
@option_group_id=8f73831d-f611-43bc-8130-4b429435967f
@option_id=8ea293e7-26ce-4eb5-8054-f53046c309c3

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
    "sku": "TIRA-002",
    "name": "Flat White",
    "type": "SIMPLE",
    "basePrice": 120000,
    "taxRate": 0.1,
    "category": {
        "id": "{{category_id}}"
    },
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "optionGroups": [
        {
            "optionGroupId": "{{option_group_id}}",
            "sortOrder": 1,
            "optionValues": [
                {
                    "optionId": "{{option_id}}",
                    "price": 20000
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
### Create Option Group & Options
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/option-groups
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
    "name": "Sugar Level",
    "isRequired": true,
    "isMultiple": false,
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "options": [
        {
            "name": "Sugar 50%",
            "basePrice": 0,
            "sortOrder": 1
        },
        {
            "name": "Sugar 70%",
            "basePrice": 0,
            "sortOrder": 2
        }
    ]
}

